{
  "stem": "3100.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, your brother had a struggle, and he was shot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Oh, when I heard this came out, believe me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I remember the Kultusminister, Auerbach, was at that time Jewish in the German government.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he came down to Amberg.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the, the detective that shot him produced a, a, a certificate that he had-- he-- that he argued with him, and he almost choked him.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He had signs on his back, and he called him Hitlerist.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then Auerbach said, this why you did it, in self-defense, right?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But why did you have to put in five bullets in him?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said, I don't remember how many.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, of course, you didn't have any witnesses to it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I know that we buried him in Amberg.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And to his funeral, if there have been not 100,000 people in this funeral, because it was advertised all over in the papers that a Jew was shot by German police because of what-- they, they came up with the whole thing.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And all the Jews that were in Munchen and in Landsberg, and-- they heard that-- and especially the [INAUDIBLE] men from Krasnik-- they all came to the funeral.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The funeral took place-- today is Wednesday, the second day of Shavuot.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember that for six miles to the cemetery, we walked.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, the, the, the, the body was on a-- on a horse and carriage.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And all, all, all others-- even, even the Germans-- walked.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Social Democrats",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--went along with this, because at that time, it was a shock to everybody.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
